#: ../../hardware/controllers/numark_mixtrack_platinum_fx.md:11
msgid ""
"The Mixtrack Platinum FX is a 24-bit 4-deck digital DJ controller with a "
"dedicated software effects section, large 6-inch capacitive-touch jog wheels"
" and 16-multifunctional performance pads. Its stand out feature  is the LCD "
"displays integrated into the jog wheels, apart from that it shares the "
"layout of the Mixtrack Pro FX."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/numark_mixtrack_platinum_fx.md:13
msgid ""
"It is a USB Audio and MIDI Class compliant device and works with Linux, "
"macOS, and Windows."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/numark_mixtrack_platinum_fx.md:15
msgid ""
"[Manufacturer's product page](https://www.numark.com/product/mixtrack-"
"platinum-fx)"
msgstr ""

